Clone the repository:
                     git clone https://github.com/your-username/currency-converter.git cd currency-converter
Install dependencies: Install the required Pillow library using pip:
                                                                   pip install Pillow
Download a background image:
                           Place a background image (e.g., background.jpg) in the project directory. You can download a free mobile app-style gradient or abstract image from sites like Unsplash or Pexels.
Recommended image size: 400x350 pixels or larger.
Update the filename in the code (bg_image = Image.open("background.jpg")) if using a different image.

Run the application:
                    python currency_converter.py
